{"tid":140864,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[學術討論][無圖]點解啲正既日本AV通常都有碼？","createTime":"2017-03-02T13:22:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-02T14:15:54.000Z","uid":56919,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e82e2677cbbc5a4cf67107becc267906edfee2bc","tid":140864,"uid":56919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T13:22:33.000Z","msg":"認真想問好耐<br />\n好似好多無碼既AV都係一啲柒既女優<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好多靚女女優都係有碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n究竟點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cd2fd8063c6c853f045c1d132d6f21dd62e24da","tid":140864,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T13:26:39.000Z","msg":"無碼犯法"},{"pid":"bdc22e71b83bc98b3c39be7d1f16605306ac9b16","tid":140864,"uid":68025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T13:28:05.000Z","msg":"但係點解又有無碼睇嘅？"},{"pid":"e605b81e0cbf9c25a0dc4f88abe6584de705b903","tid":140864,"uid":56919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T13:58:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但係點解又有無碼睇嘅？</blockquote><br />\n我都唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcf1c1d639ec9709f0b249aa5eade7cfec364dac","tid":140864,"uid":36839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T14:01:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>但係點解又有無碼睇嘅？</blockquote><br />\n我都唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無碼無記錯就係啲av片商係外國註冊<br />\n用外國片商個名黎發行，賣番日本"},{"pid":"1e635977e21afc4103b9d65e097d69282ba50f8f","tid":140864,"uid":33040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T14:02:42.000Z","msg":"點解正既女都唔俾我屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4269efb451ffc9af83f7b6979fd14d787aa6795","tid":140864,"uid":5572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T14:03:40.000Z","msg":"因為如果無碼同有碼一樣咁清 唔會有人睇有碼 所以要降低有碼質素"},{"pid":"9aedcf8ec4c76c80fbcc4b8e21dd0554cd519148","tid":140864,"uid":5572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T14:04:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為如果無碼同有碼一樣咁清 唔會有人睇有碼 所以要降低<span style=\"color: red;\">無</span>碼質素</blockquote>"},{"pid":"dcf92dc2fe7f235a31c42f2850fc270129b9c009","tid":140864,"uid":56919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T14:14:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>但係點解又有無碼睇嘅？</blockquote><br />\n我都唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無碼無記錯就係啲av片商係外國註冊<br />\n用外國片商個名黎發行，賣番日本</blockquote><br />\n即係淨係日本發行果啲一定要有碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b04751cc8a674a4383c829e8a828e1d93d5bbe1","tid":140864,"uid":56919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T14:15:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>因為如果無碼同有碼一樣咁清 唔會有人睇有碼 所以要降低<span style=\"color: red;\">無</span>碼質素</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n照你咁講一開始賣無碼咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}